results.name: a(n) = -A085466(n) times the free coefficient of the 2n-th Du Bois-Reymond polynomial in e^2.
mathematica: a = {7}; Do[p = FullSimplify[TrigToExp[ -3 - 2Residue[x^2/((Tan[x] - x) (1 + x^2)^n), {x, I}]]]; AppendTo[a, -First[p[[2]]]], {n, 2, 9}]; a (*Artur Jasinski*)
